The paper focuses on the application of deep reinforcement learning in communications and networking, which involves both machine learning (cs.LG) and networking (cs.NI) concepts. The paper also discusses the use of deep learning (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY) in the context of reinforcement learning. Additionally, the paper addresses network security (cs.CR), which is a sub-category of computer security. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.NI, followed by cs.AI, cs.SY, and cs.CR.
